messages.message:
@Aayush If it's not too late, can we leave out the "< 1 MB"? I just got some more details in the ticket and realize that that part isn't specifically relevant to this option. Also, if I'm understanding those notes right, this doesn't affect non-Excel spreadsheets (like Google sheets), so let's add "Excel" back in.

So it should read:
[ ] *Process spreadsheets natively*
Processes Excel spreadsheets in their native file format instead of converting to PDF. This option offers better results for wide tables, but doesn't support source detection.
